<plot>A man wakes up every morning, goes to work everyday, goes to sleep every night, but remains detached from the real world. He keeps himself sedated throughout the time by listening to talk radio, watching news and talking to friends about "important issues." Finally he is literally knocked in the head by reality, and he wakes up.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?052891</url></doc>
